name: Invesco 1-5 Year Laddered Investment Grade Corporate Bond Index ETF
longDescription: PSB seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses the performance of the FTSE Canada Investment Grade 15 Year Laddered Corporate Bond Index or any successor thereto. This Invesco ETF invests primarily in Canadian investmentgrade corporate bonds. PIB seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE Canada Investment Grade 1 10 Year Laddered Corporate Bond Index, or any successor thereto. This Invesco ETF invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in Canadian investment grade corporate bonds.
